videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan Jr. drives into the lane and throws a lob to Jalen Smith for the alley-oop connection.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Smith flushes alley-oop for Maryland) 2020/01/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith flushes alley-oop for Maryland

videos.description: Jalen Smith rejects a shot at the rim and Maryland runs out in transition, leading to Anthony Cowan Jr.'s 3-pointer that gives Maryland its first lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maryland turns defense into offense for 1st lead) 2020/01/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland turns defense into offense for 1st lead
